mv,Maldives,Finance,6015,1,6553987435,FaisaMobile X by MIB,Maldives Islamic Bank Private Limited,https://apps.apple.com/mv/app/faisamobile-x-by-mib/id6553987435?uo=4,0.0,3.3,10,Finance,"Introducing FaisaMobile X – where eXperiment meets eXperience!

FaisaMobile X brings mobile banking with a refreshed design and enhanced features. Switch seamlessly between personal, business, and other profiles, giving you full control of all your banking needs with FaisaMobile X – the all-new, user-friendly, and secure mobile banking app by Maldives Islamic Bank (MIB).
Get started with FaisaMobile X by logging in with your FaisaNet Username and Password.

column2: Don't have a FaisaNet account? Register online on FaisaMobile X or at faisanet.mib.com.mv.
New to MIB? Open an account instantly online at applynow.mib.com.mv and start banking.

column1: [Key Features]
o
column2: Multi-profile Banking
Bank with your personal, kids, business, and joint accounts with easy switching between them.

column1: o
column2: Enhanced Home Screen
View and swipe between all your accounts, their balances and history (Pssstt! If you don’t want prying eyes on your balances, just hide it by enabling Privacy Mode!).
Quickly switch between all your profiles.
Initiate transfers from any account.
View pending approvals (for business and jointly managed accounts).
Customizable shortcuts to quickly access your favorite banking functions.
View notifications.

column1: o
column2: Enhanced Business Banking
Bank with your team with streamlined maker and approval workflows.
Make bulk transfers for salaries and other payments, view their progress, status, and history.

column1: o
column2: Enhanced Accounts Screen
View details of all your accounts, balances, transactions, and statements.
Initiate transfers from any account.
View, save and share transaction receipts.
Sort and filter transactions for simplified viewing.
Customize your accounts and give them a personality with lively backgrounds (available on FaisaNet).

column1: o
column2: Enhanced Transfers Screen
Make instant quick transfers with enhanced and verified search using account numbers (MIB and other Favara participant banks), Favara ID, or beneficiary names.
Make transfers between your accounts, to other MIB accounts and other bank accounts with Favara.
Schedule transfers for one-time and recurring future transfers.
View and manage scheduled transfers.
Enhanced SWIFT transfers and large-amount transfers with supporting documents.

column1: o
column2: Enhanced Beneficiary Management
Manage your favorite accounts (beneficiaries) and customize them with profile pictures.
Manage beneficiary categories to better organize beneficiaries of your loved ones, businesses, and for everyone!

column1: Plus, enjoy all your favorite FaisaMobile features.
o
column2: Easily Manage Your Cards
View all your debit cards.
Activate your cards.
Change your card PIN.
Freeze your cards temporarily.
Block your cards permanently.

column1: o
column2: Instant Inter-Bank Transfers with Favara
Make Favara Transfers to other local banks instantly.
Make Favara Requests to request funds from your friends, family and businesses.
Accept and decline Favara Requests from others.
Make Recalls of Favara Transfers that you made in error.
Accept and decline Favara Transfer Recalls from others.
Manage your Favara IDs to save your accounts as your phone number, email address or national ID.

column1: o
column2: Financing Facilities at a Glance
View full details of your financing facilities.

column1: o
column2: Manage Cheques
View all your cheque books and cheques.
Report lost cheques and cheque books.

column1: o
column2: Get in Touch with Us Quickly
Chat live with our Customer Care for online requests and queries.
Find the nearest branches and ATMs.

column1: o
column2: Be Assured of Industry-standard Security.
FaisaMobile uses industry-standard security methods to ensure all your information, transactions and everything done through the app are done securely.
Use OTPs via SMS and mobile authenticator apps for both logins and transfers.
Use PIN and biometrics to unlock FaisaMobile X.
Completely clear any saved data.

column1: mv,Maldives,Finance,6015,2,1374223530,FaisaMobile by MIB,Maldives Islamic Bank Private Limited,https://apps.apple.com/mv/app/faisamobile-by-mib/id1374223530?uo=4,0.0,2.875,24,Finance,"Be in control of all your accounts, financing, cheques and all your Bank-related stuff on FaisaMobile; an all-in-one modern, user friendly and secure mobile banking app by MIB. Quickly check you account balances, account histories, make transfers, view your financing facilities, manage your cheques, contact the Bank and so much more on FaisaMobile, whether you're on the move or curled up on your sofa.
FaisaMobile is the latest addition to the online banking service channels of Maldives Islamic Bank. All aspects of your online banking experience are beautifully packaged into one convenient app.
User your FaisaNet (our internet banking service) Username and Password to get started with FaisaMobile. Don't have a FaisaNet account? Register online on FaisaMobile or at faisanet.mib.com.mv.
Here are some highlights of what you can do with FaisaMobile.
• View your accounts and transactions with a swipe
- View all your accounts and account balances
- View detailed account statements and transactions
- Save and share account transactions
- Sort and filter account transactions for simplified viewing
• View your cards and manage them
- View all your debit cards
- Activate your cards
- Change your card PIN
- Freeze your cards temporarily
- Block your cards permanently
• Make transfers with a drag and drop!
- Make transfers to your favorite people with a simple drag and drop
- Make quick transfers to unsaved accounts
- Do transfers within your accounts, to other MIB accounts and other bank accounts
- Manage your favorite accounts and account categories
• Make instant inter-bank transfers with Favara
- Make Favara Transfers to your favorite people in other local banks instantly
- Make Favara Requests to request funds from your friends, family and businesses
- Accept and decline Favara Requests from others
- Make Recalls of Favara Transfers that you made in error
- Accept and decline Favara Transfer Recalls from others
- Manage your Favara IDs to save your accounts as your phone number, email address or national ID
• View all your financing facilities at a glance
- View all your financing facilities in brief and in full detail
- Check facility paid amount, balance, installment amount, last paid date and more
• View all your cheque books and cheques with ease
- View status of all your cheque books and their cheques
- View individual cheque details
- Report lost cheques and cheque books
• Get in touch with us quickly
- Send quick messages to us for any online requests and queries
- Call us, send an SMS to us, visit our website and view our Facebook, Twitter and Instagram pages
- Find the nearest branches and ATMs
• Be assured of industry-standard security
- FaisaMobile uses industry-standard security methods to ensure all your information, transactions and everything done through the app are done securely
- Use PIN and fingerprint to unlock FaisaMobile
- Change PIN and fingerprint whenever needed
- Completely clear any saved data

mv,Maldives,Finance,6015,13,6502288497,Elirox - AI Trading Bot,Elirox LLC,https://apps.apple.com/mv/app/elirox-ai-trading-bot/id6502288497?uo=4,0.0,1,1,Finance,"Elirox is an automated trading app that helps you trade smart and simple. EASY TO START
With Elirox, trading becomes easier. Start automating your trades in a few steps:
- Choose an asset (currency, index, share, or another financial instrument).
- Set up trading parameters yourself, or make it even easier with the AI assistant—it selects the settings for your strategy based on your chosen asset and investment amount.
- Start the bot and check the results in detailed analytics.
CUSTOMIZE YOUR TRADING STRATEGY

- Modify risk management settings to protect your investments effectively.
- Use advanced trading filters to automatically stop the bot when needed.
- Visualize your trading algorithm with convenient real-time charts that track live market quotes.
SEAMLESS BROKER INTEGRATION

Linking your broker to Elirox is quick and easy, whether you use Doto, Exness, or another platform. The intuitive interface guides you through each step, making account setup smooth so you can start trading in minutes.
TRY A DEMO FIRST
If you’d like to practice first, you can start with a demo account. It comes with virtual funds, letting you experiment with the bots and see how they work—without any risk.
- Practice and explore how the app works without any risk.
- Get comfortable with the features before trading with real money.
GET SUPPORT
Our customer support team is here to help with any questions. Use our guides to learn about all the settings and possibilities, or reach out to us via email or live chat.

mv,Maldives,Finance,6015,19,1231393474,YONO SBI:Banking and Lifestyle,State Bank of India,https://apps.apple.com/mv/app/yono-sbi-banking-and-lifestyle/id1231393474?uo=4,0.0,4.2,5,Finance,"YONO SBI: Bank, Invest, Shop, Travel, Pay Bills, Recharge, use UPI to transfer money

Download YONO SBI, our mobile banking and lifestyle application from iOS App store only and experience its best-in-class features. Do not use any other websites.
Registration process:
YONO is supported on iOS 15 and above.
• Install/update new version of App from App Store and open.
• Allow all required permission (location).
• Select SIM of CBS Registered Mobile Number (RMN) and submit NEXT.

• An encrypted SMS with a unique code will be sent from the device to Bank’s VMN (Virtual Mobile Number) to verify the customer. Kindly note that for sending the SMS standard SMS charges are applicable as per your telecom plan. The SIM should have an active outgoing SMS facility.
• If there are multiple CIF's attached with same mobile number, system will prompt for the account number and DOB for finding out a unique customer by the mobile number.

• If the customer is already having online banking facility of SBI, App will automatically prompt to proceed to register on YONO SBI app with existing user credentials (Online Banking User ID and Password). After entering User ID and Password, customer will receive an OTP on Registered Mobile Number. User has to enter the OTP in the app to complete registration with an optional setting of MPIN.
• If the existing SBI customer is not having Online banking credentials, App will prompt to proceed to create INB credential using ""Account Details"" and ""ATM Card"" based registration process.

• If Non RMN SIM is selected, user will land on account opening screen. If customer claims that selected SIM is already registered with bank, user needs to visit nearest branch with KYC for updating/ validating the mobile number in bank account.
What YONO SBI offers you

YONO SBI, SBI's latest mobile banking offering is an extension of our trusted banking legacy which gave India secure digital products such as YONO Lite and SBI Net Banking. YONO SBI puts India's largest range of products and services at your fingertips.

• Liquidity on the go-Use this one click facility to avail overdraft against Fixed Deposit
• Experience convenience: Request Cheque Books, ATM Cards/Debit Cards or use the emergency services to change ATM PIN, block ATM cards/Debit cards or stop cheques, through YONO SBI

• Investments - Open Investment account and make investments
